    include nav
    .container
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          p.kind Photoshop
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          p.projects Brandy Clark Album Release Invite
          a(href='http://www.brandyclarkmusic.com', target='_blank')
            img.img-responsive.photoshop(src='img/BC Evite 10.29.jpg', alt='Brandy Clark Album Release Invite')
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          p.projects Patrick Joseph Showcase E-Blast
          a(href='https://www.facebook.com/PJMSongs', target='_blank')
            img.img-responsive.photoshop(src='img/PJM Writers night 6.jpg', alt="Patrick Joseph Music Writer's Night e blast")
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          p.projects Hits Magazine Ad
          a(href='http://www.warnerchappell.com', target='_blank')
            img.img-responsive.photoshop(src='img/HITSad3Small.jpg', alt='Warner Chappell Hits Magazine Ad')
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          p.projects Music Row magazine Ad
          a(href='#', target='_blank')
            img.img-responsive.photoshop(src='img/Josh Turner.jpg', alt='Music Row Magazine Ad featuring Josh Turner')
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          p.projects NashvesTN Mobile Splash Screens
          a(href='http://nashvestn.herokuapp.com/', target='_blank')
            img.img-responsive.photoshop(src='img/nashvesTNlogoLandscape.png', alt='Front page of the NashvesTN application')
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          p.projects Company Web Page
          a(href='http://www.salonstellanashville.com/', target='_blank')
            img.img-responsive.photoshop(src='img/salonstella.png', alt='Front page of a client website for Salon Stella Nashville')
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          p.projects Gravity Flip Mobile Splash Screens
          a(href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=daveboling.gravity.flip&hl=en', target='_blank')
            img.img-responsive.photoshop(src='img/gravityFlip 1024.jpg', alt='Icon for Gravity Flip game')
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          p.projects All Access Pass
          a(href='#', target='_blank')
            img.img-responsive.photoshop(src='img/BrandyClarkAllAccess.jpg', alt='All Access Pass for Brandy Clark')
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          p.kind Video
      .row.border
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8
          p.projects
            | Getting To Know Brandy Clark
            .embed-responsive.embed-responsive-16by9
              iframe.embed-responsive-item(src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/7twxI4hmPhA', allowfullscreen='allowfullscreen')
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
          p.description
            | This is a video for Warner Bros. recording artist Brandy Clark where Sarah filmed, and edited the video of Brandy's team. Edited with Final Cut Express
      .row.border
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8
          p.projects
            | Jingle Strong Documentary
            .embed-responsive.embed-responsive-16by9
              iframe.embed-responsive-item(src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/YbNz_GcnOJ8', allowfullscreen='allowfullscreen')
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
          p.description
            | This is a video for Music City Jamboree.  Sarah was a videographer for this project.
